OL,3,CHirwaun man jailed for causing death
OL,4,Cof teenager by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA family has spoken of their
OL,7,Fdetermination to make sure no other
OL,8,Ffamily has to go through what they did
OL,9,Fas a man from has been jailed after
OL,10,Fpleading guilty to causing death by
OL,11,Fdangerous driving.
OL,13,FKaylan Hippsley, 13, from Hirwaun,
OL,14,Fdied three days after being hit by a
OL,15,Fcar driven by Harley Whiteman on
OL,16,FBrecon Road, Hirwaun, Rhondda Cynon
OL,17,FTaf, on 29 February.
