OL,3,CHirwaun man jailed for causing death
OL,4,Cof teenager by dangerous driving
OL,6,FNineteen-year-old Whiteman from Cae
OL,7,FFelin Parc, Hirwaun, was sentenced to
OL,8,Fsix years and nine months' detention
OL,9,Fin a young offender institution for
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving after
OL,11,Fpleading guilty at Merthyr Tydfil
OL,12,FCrown Court on Tuesday, 30 April.
OL,14,FPolice released CCTV footage of the
OL,15,Fmoments leading up to the collision,
OL,16,Fshowing the Ford Fiesta Whiteman was
OL,17,Fdriving speeding down a road.
OL,19,FKaylan's family have paid tribute to
OL,20,Fhim, saying they had been processing
OL,21,Fhis death "with great difficulty".
