OL,6,FThey stated: "Kaylan was such a cheeky
OL,7,Fchappie. He always had a twinkle in
OL,8,Fhis eye and could get away with
OL,9,Fanything with his smile and quick wit.
OL,11,FHis cousin Julie said "he was very
OL,12,Fwitty, he had a real funny sense of
OL,13,Fhumour. he was loving, he was a lovely
OL,14,Fbrother.
OL,16,F"When we were sitting there holding
OL,17,Fhis hand you could still smell his
OL,18,Faftershave on him, the product in his
OL,19,Fhair. All that was still present, he
OL,20,Fjust looked like a little boy.
