OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F464A1714741909
OL,3,CHirwaun man jailed for causing death
OL,4,Cof teenager by dangerous driving
OL,6,F"It's just unbelievable that he's been
OL,7,Ftook from us in such a cruel way.
OL,9,FBut they're unhappy with the length of
OL,10,Fthe sentence handed to Whiteman.
OL,12,FJulie said, "It just feels like it's a
OL,13,Fjoke.
OL,15,F"We promised him we'd do everything we
OL,16,Fcould to get justice for him, and it
OL,17,Ffeels like we've been slapped in the
OL,18,Fface."
