OL,4,Cof teenager by dangerous driving
OL,6,FKaylan was involved in the local rugby
OL,7,Fclub and now a tournament is planned
OL,8,Ffor the summer, called "Kaylan's Cup".
OL,10,FHis family said in a statement,
OL,11,F"Kaylan was a talented rugby and
OL,12,Ffootball player. He loved on-line
OL,13,Fgaming. He was a bright, intelligent
OL,14,Fboy and a much-loved pupil in Aberdare
OL,15,FCommunity School....we are devastated
OL,16,Fto lose Kaylan at such a young age,
OL,17,Fonly 13 with his whole life ahead of
OL,18,Fhim.
